{"tid":1591194,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[巴絲留意]我哋開始比人包圍","createTime":"2019-09-24T05:06:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-24T05:51:41.000Z","uid":259017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"96b47fbe819d461b9a6a6756f9b6dcfcb6cdb66e","tid":1591194,"uid":259017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T05:06:10.000Z","msg":"臨近國㷫，對家傳媒戰手法開始升級<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n1.多日多人跳樓浮屍就係為左令你哋開始情感麻木,偏向追究警暴,令之前發生醫院系統漏洞,基本法指出香港有普選等大問題被忽視<br />\n2.議員被捕被襲,令議員人人自危,減少阻礙狗方清場,狗方拉夠人有交代<br />\n3.狗方黑衣做勇武,混淆我方士氣,令和理非質疑係咪勇武做時,勇武因要出嚟澄清,士氣低落<br />\n而家對家就擺明係抄我哋,我哋就更需要思想上Be Water,創造新式戰略,回歸及重提運動五大訴求<br />\n兄弟爬山,各有各做<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf187a46663ac33055cc188826cd192ffa8f1c40","tid":1591194,"uid":259017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T05:06:41.000Z","msg":"推（1/10）"},{"pid":"d951359531c356cf5ef87082f5cf53ad6b303138","tid":1591194,"uid":259017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T05:06:51.000Z","msg":"推（2/10）"},{"pid":"c943d0f6c900a28e6b1248619f8fd9b8bca87dd6","tid":1591194,"uid":259017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T05:07:02.000Z","msg":"推（3/10）"},{"pid":"8bbb4cad858172b0a2087d51cf4bfa6788431c01","tid":1591194,"uid":259017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T05:07:19.000Z","msg":"推（4/10）"},{"pid":"f87b71e72b832aadddb03afd027d36019fb5621c","tid":1591194,"uid":259017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T05:07:38.000Z","msg":"推（5/10）"},{"pid":"6f87bcabe89a9d428bf5e1c15fc3bbcce6f34fcc","tid":1591194,"uid":259017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T05:07:51.000Z","msg":"推（6/10）"},{"pid":"752595423a469dfb33a66f44e7744c617580fe12","tid":1591194,"uid":259017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T05:08:03.000Z","msg":"推（7/10）"},{"pid":"6f03146c5c593511acd